caption: (Translated by Google) Crispy Pata 17.99 is not freshly cooked and the meat is too hard to eat. Next time, don't sell it when it's old. What is expensive is not fresh.  (Original) Crispy Pata 17.99  hindi naman bagong luto pati yung meat nya sobrang tigas na hindi makain. Next time naman wag ng ibenta pag luma na. Ang mahal mahal di naman fresh.
Always bought a chitcharon bulaklak there but I made  my own  sauce in our house, don't like their sauce.
Gave them a try side dish was good salt and pepper shrimp was big and tasty . Ukoy was 3.50 for a cold soggy piece told them and they didn’t offer to make it up.
